    "title": "JSW Steel Global Group is Hiring: Quality Control Engineer (Principal)",
    "description": "If you're a passionate Quality Control Engineer with drive and ambition, JSW Steel Global Group in Ahmedabad is the place for you. We're growing fast and need talented people to grow with us.\n\nAbout JSW Steel Global Group:\nJSW Steel Global Group is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Train and supervise shop floor workers and supervisors\n• Prepare production cost analysis and efficiency reports\n• Ensure environmental compliance and waste management\n• Monitor equipment performance and coordinate preventive maintenance\n• Coordinate with design and engineering teams on product improvements\n• Conduct root cause analysis for quality rejections and defects\n• Coordinate with logistics for dispatching finished goods\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Post Graduate Diploma in relevant field\n• 1-3 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in AutoCAD\n• Proficiency in PLC/SCADA\n• Proficiency in PPAP\n• Proficiency in SolidWorks\n• Proficiency in SAP MM/PP\n• Proficiency in Lean Manufacturing\n• Proficiency in Project Management\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain Management\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Salary Range: 4 LPA - 9 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Ahmedabad, Gujarat, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with JSW Steel Global Group!",
